textDelta: What is always true of a spontaneous process: exothermic, no work, system entropy increases, system entropy and surroundings increase? The spontaneous process always increases entropy.

What was the Clinton Administration's policy on the Russian economy? The Clinton Administration's policy was to support the Russian economy and to encourage Russian investment in the United States.

During the Clinton administration, did the US promote the marketization of the Russian economy? The US promoted the marketization of the Russian economy during the Clinton administration.
